These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
There 3 different types of food: spinach, apricot, peach
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, daffodil
1. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person who growsamaryllis##7
2. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
3. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Food   | peach | apricot | spinach |
| Flower           | amaryllis  | daffodil     | dahlia  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, fisherman, mechanic
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, soy-milk
1. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
2. the videographer is somewhere between the mechanic and the person drinking juice##7
3. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Job   | fisherman | videographer | mechanic |
| Beverage     | juice       | soy-milk     | tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, comedy, spy
City: london, hannover, nizza
1. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person traveling to london##7
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre    | drama | comedy | spy  |
| City   | nizza  | hannover  | london |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, dog, bird
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, british
1. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the british and the owner of the dog##7
2. the mexican is not the owner of the fish##6
3. the british is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Pet           | dog | fish | bird     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | brazilian          | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
3 different games are played: chess, domino, mah-jongg
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, police-officer, bartender
1. the police-officer is somewhere between the bartender and the person playing domino##7
2. the project-manager is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the police-officer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Game   | chess      | mah-jongg     | domino   |
| Job     | bartender | police-officer | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, card-games, gardening
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, tower
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
2. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the tower house and the person who's hobby is singing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | gardening    | card-games     | singing     |
| House   | tower | cape-cod | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
