.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, rock, funk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, march, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the fan disco##3
2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the fan rock##7
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fan disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Music-Genre           | funk | disco  | rock |
| Birthday   | january      | august | march      |

