.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, musical, fantasy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, ambient, pop
1. the fan pop is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
2. the fan ambient is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the fan funk is somewhere between the fan ambient and the person watching musical movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | fantasy | romance   |
| Music-Genre     | pop    | funk  | ambient |

