.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, helicopter
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, nigerian, french
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the french is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the nigerian##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Transport   | motorbike   | helicopter    | trike |
| Nationality      | french | egyptian | nigerian |

