.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, taxi
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, guinea-pig
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person driving the taxi##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Transport         | taxi | bus | snowmobile |
| Pet   | turtle    | guinea-pig    | hedgehog         |

