City: venice, hannover, hamburg
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to venice is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the farmhouse house##7
3. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| House          | farmhouse  | cottage       | wooden     |
| City   | hamburg | venice | hannover |

