2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person playing domino is somewhere between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who growsrose##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Flower        | orchid | dahlia | rose |
| Game   | mah-jongg  | domino       | monopoly      |

