2. the dunhill-smoker is the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere between the person who growslily and the person who growsbegonia##7
4. the person who growsbegonia is the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar          | dunhill | bluemaster     | game   |
| Flower   | lily   | daisy | begonia |

