.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
3 different games are played: canasta, poker, mah-jongg
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, roller, tram
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person driving the roller##7
3. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Game   | poker      | mah-jongg     | canasta |
| Transport        | tram | bike | roller    |

 